NUMBER 2372
NAME Arch at the edge of the village
ASTRAL
CHANNEL 556

*DESCRIPTION_START
The arch is carved of a stone with a different grain and color than the
surrounding mountainside, and yet it seems part of the slope itself, merging
smoothly with the stone both above and below the narrow path. Glittering
lines of gold and silver run through its outmost surface, also smooth and
natural, the metal a part of the stone. Below the path by a short distance,
the silvery mist clings to the mountain slope, unnatural and bringing a
sweet, sharp smell to your nostrils.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB FLY -1
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER As soon as you begin to rise off the ground, you feel a curious weakness. Silvery mist surrounds your body, leeching away your strength the moment you are no longer in contact with the protective surface of the planet.
        ECHO OTHERS Silver mist writhes out of nowhere, surrounding %n!
        EQUAL FATPOINTS 0
        EQUAL PSIPOINTS 0
        EQUAL MANAPOINTS 0
        EQUAL BODYPOINTS 10
        EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
ENDIF

EXIT SW 2371

ITEM 0 60 ADJ1=7 ADJ2=312 VAL2=2373




NUMBER 2373
NAME Mountainside ledge
ASTRAL
CHANNEL 556

*DESCRIPTION_START
The mountainside is rough and new, hardly worn at all by the actions of
wind and weather. While the dragons are an ancient race, even the youngest
of these mountains has been here much, much longer. Despite the dips and
curves in the slope, the path itself, smooth as glass beneath your feet
from the passage of those who have come before so many times, remains
absolutely level. So too does the layer of silver mist, just out of
reach, like the surface of an enchanted lake filling the valley below.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB FLY -1
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER As soon as you begin to rise off the ground, you feel a curious weakness. Silvery mist surrounds your body, leeching away your strength the moment you are no longer in contact with the protective surface of the planet.
        ECHO OTHERS Silver mist writhes out of nowhere, surrounding %n!
        EQUAL FATPOINTS 0
        EQUAL PSIPOINTS 0
        EQUAL MANAPOINTS 0
        EQUAL BODYPOINTS 10
        EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
ENDIF

EXIT SW 2372
EXIT N 2374


NUMBER 2374
NAME Mountainside ledge, bridge
ASTRAL
CHANNEL 556

*DESCRIPTION_START
At some point in its ancient history, the path was shattered by a blast
of lightning or perhaps the action of a careless dragon, and for a distance
of a dozen paces or so the mountainside is a sheer cliff. A bridge was built
by the Korvatae, dragons needing no bridges, of course. It is unlike the
workmanship of the arch which marks the beginning of the path, made from
quarried stone instead of magically shaped, and shows much less of the
smooth, worn look that the rest of the trail possesses. The mists below
churn as though disturbed by something, but retain their level.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB FLY -1
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER As soon as you begin to rise off the ground, you feel a curious weakness. Silvery mist surrounds your body, leeching away your strength the moment you are no longer in contact with the protective surface of the planet.
        ECHO OTHERS Silver mist writhes out of nowhere, surrounding %n!
        EQUAL FATPOINTS 0
        EQUAL PSIPOINTS 0
        EQUAL MANAPOINTS 0
        EQUAL BODYPOINTS 10
        EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
ENDIF

EXIT S 2373

