NUMBER 2376
NAME Wide Ledge before the Temple
CHANNEL 556
ASTRAL

*DESCRIPTION_START
The ledge is wider here than the bridge to the south, much wider. It is
actually large enough for several dragons to land or stand, presumeably
because they do exactly that. Before you is the entrance of the Hall of
the Silent Ones, an opening in the mountainside made remarkable only
by its sheer size. The height of the mist is unchanged, but it seems
closer, for the stones here are so worn as to have actually lowered
the level of the ledge itself over time.
*DESCRIPTION_END

