NUMBER 2382
NAME Astral space
DEEPCAVE
CHANNEL 557

*DESCRIPTION_START
You are bodiless, the form you seem to inhabit a simple construction
of astral mist and your own memories of your shape. Only your mind has
substance here, and yet it is powerful substance. You sense that you
can manipulate the environment, with sufficient effort, though you
have no skill in this art.
*DESCRIPTION_END

