NUMBER 2383
NAME Astral space
DEEPCAVE
CHANNEL 557

*DESCRIPTION_START
You are bodiless, yet you have the power to move and shape all that
is. Only the forms of other intelligences are not vulnerable to your
mental commands... if only you knew exactly how to make those commands
with the proper authority and skill. Through the astral mists you can
see distant scenes, hear echoes of past and present, perhaps even
the future...
*DESCRIPTION_END

