NUMBER 2384
NAME Astral space
ASTRAL
CHANNEL 557

*DESCRIPTION_START
You are bodiless. This disturbs you not at all, for you know that your
corporeal form is as safe as any mortal can ever be, within the temple
which houses the Hall of the Silent Ones. The mists wreathe your
imaginary form, slave to your untrained will.
*DESCRIPTION_END

EXIT U 2383
EXIT D 2385

;
;

NUMBER 2385
NAME Astral space
ASTRAL
CHANNEL 557

*DESCRIPTION_START
You are bodiless, but the world around you has provided you with a
shape. You suspect that it is not quite the same as your true one, for
it is a thing of your memories and who really knows one's true appearance
in every detail? Still, it suffices, and the mists respond to your motions,
shape themselves to your tentative desires.
*DESCRIPTION_END

EXIT D 2386
EXIT O 2384

;
