NUMBER 2386
NAME Astral space
ASTRAL
CHANNEL 557

*DESCRIPTION_START
A column of black and white, thin lines swirling within and around each
other, so small as to form a gray surface at a distance, dances through the
mists here. It does not disturb the astral vapor in any way, dancing alone
and untouchable.
*DESCRIPTION_END

